# 5. VM Resources
- 2 CPU with Acceleration
- RAM 1024 mb
- Video RAM 64m
- HDD SATA AHCI Virtual size 64 Gb (1,73 Gb Real size)
- Network mode NAT

# 6 VM customize
Settings
> v.memory = 2048
> v.cpus = 4

